{"tid":544913,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[An]寫左隻android新聞app,方便速讀新聞同各類資訊","createTime":"2018-01-30T04:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T11:42:26.000Z","uid":168697,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9882e6b09084cbc40a6d55a2fb394db234e93e","tid":544913,"uid":168697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WZOfvG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWZOfvG2.png&h=ea536c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eQ2pdKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeQ2pdKC.png&h=1e11ee90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XVCkNj0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXVCkNj0.png&h=a25cc1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依隻app係Android既rss reader,可以係1隻app入面好快速咁睇到各類資訊<br />\n<br />\n隻app嘅特點:<br />\n1. 其它RSS reader只可以建立單層既群組結構,而依隻app可以建立多層既群組結構,容易將大量嘅新聞源分類<br />\n2. App入面已經內建左下面嘅新聞feeds,仲有好多其它類別既feeds,唔洗巴打絲打周圍搵feeds:<br />\n-明報<br />\n-信報<br />\n-經濟日報<br />\n-東方日報<br />\n-蘋果日報<br />\n-RTHK<br />\n-頭條日報<br />\n-都市日報<br />\n-晴報<br />\n-香港政府新聞網<br />\n3. app既設計係方便大家速讀新聞同其它資訊<br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴打絲打試用,亦都可以比啲意見,黎緊會加入更多功能,同埋會美化隻APP<br />\n另外隻app岩岩上架,可能會有啲唔穩定或者bugs,請大家見諒,大家可以係度反映返啲問題同bugs<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/oKtHGN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FoKtHGN&d=BfQSKVsVgyFtsp%2BxWUngPJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=df8df657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/oKtHGN</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fernonion.newsforest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.fernonion.newsforest&d=BfQSKVsVgyFtsp%2BxWUngPJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0e7e98c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fernonion.newsforest</a>"},{"pid":"56c145d6eac4567dc7958792fe858b05e171471e","tid":544913,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d436d76f20a950a391f71b54813948ba70ba61b","tid":544913,"uid":168697,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"56c145d6eac4567dc7958792fe858b05e171471e","tid":544913,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:20:10.000Z","msg":"絲打好快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a3102a4dac7e89c97d02b4dfa9c628a7c6fbaf","tid":544913,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"抄Feedly?"},{"pid":"bccad35220af1f33cf55864605a4f56aeef5f637","tid":544913,"uid":124471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"好耐以前有類既app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966cbb00274d083f743217d3430ee8b884c6e6e8","tid":544913,"uid":168697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a3102a4dac7e89c97d02b4dfa9c628a7c6fbaf","tid":544913,"uid":72228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"抄Feedly?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"同feedly係同類app,隻app既layout同feedly唔同,巴打可以試用下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66e44dd9984ff447af9fd233ed2bb02754d1a41","tid":544913,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:32:46.000Z","msg":"唔錯，not bad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a919e87003cf3a52104aa95518a1006d820a1f0e","tid":544913,"uid":168697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccad35220af1f33cf55864605a4f56aeef5f637","tid":544913,"uid":124471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"好耐以前有